fields.name: Effect:
fields.value: Attack a player for 2 HP of damage. Apply 1 phase of your choice of Exhausted or Weakened if not defended.

fields.name: Upgraded:
fields.value:
Attack a player for 4 HP of damage. Apply 1 phase of your choice of Exhausted or Weakened, regardless whether the target defended or not.

*Status takes effect next phase. Read <#1191650444594909354> for more information on player statuses.*
